{"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Type Method","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"setEmails:completion:","kind":"identifier"}],"externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)setEmails:completion:","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"text":"setEmails:completion:","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","symbolKind":"method","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"title":"setEmails:completion:"},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setEmails:completion:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"sections":[],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setemails:completion:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"abstract":[{"text":"Registers multiple email addresses with completion handler.","type":"text"}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"+ (","kind":"text"},{"text":"void","preciseIdentifier":"c:v","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setEmails:","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSArray","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"NSArray"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"text":"emails","kind":"internalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"completion:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"void","preciseIdentifier":"c:v","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":" (^"},{"text":")(","kind":"text"},{"text":"NSError","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSError"},{"text":" * ","kind":"text"},{"text":"error","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":")) ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"completion"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"languages":["occ"]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Array of email address strings."}]}],"name":"emails"},{"name":"completion","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Block called when the operation completes."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Receives nil on success, or an NSError on failure."}]}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","anchor":"discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Same as ","type":"text"},{"code":"setEmails:","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" but provides callback when the server registration completes."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Use this for confirmation UI or to chain dependent operations.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Example","text":"Example","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Import emails from third-party login with confirmation:","type":"text"}]},{"code":["class SocialLoginHandler {","","    func handleGoogleSignIn(_ user: GIDGoogleUser) {","        var emails: [String] = []","","        \/\/ Primary email from Google","        if let email = user.profile?.email {","            emails.append(email)","        }","","        \/\/ Additional emails from Google profile if available","        if let additionalEmails = user.profile?.additionalEmails {","            emails.append(contentsOf: additionalEmails)","        }","","        Pushwoosh.configure.setEmails(emails) { error in","            if let error = error {","                Analytics.track(\"email_sync_failed\", properties: [","                    \"provider\": \"google\",","                    \"email_count\": emails.count,","                    \"error\": error.localizedDescription","                ])","                return","            }","","            Analytics.track(\"email_sync_success\", properties: [","                \"provider\": \"google\",","                \"email_count\": emails.count","            ])","","            \/\/ Set user ID from Google","            Pushwoosh.configure.setUserId(user.userID ?? \"\")","        }","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"}]}],"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","title":"PushwooshCore","kind":"symbol","role":"collection","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore","type":"topic"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration","abstract":[],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"PWConfiguration","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"PWConfiguration"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/setEmails:completion:":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setEmails:completion:","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"Registers multiple email addresses with completion handler.","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setemails:completion:","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"setEmails:completion:"}],"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setEmails:completion:"}],"title":"setEmails:completion:"}}}